  %div.project.fakedynamo
    %div
      %h2
        FakeDynamo
        %a{href: "https://github.com/ananthakumaran/fake_dynamo"} github.com/ananthakumaran/fake_dynamo
      %div.description
        An In-memory dynamodb emulator for
        %a{href: "http://aws.amazon.com/dynamodb/"} Amazon DynamoDB.
        We build it to help us develop applications on  dynamodb in development and test environments without incurring the costs and the latencies. This also allows us to host the non production versions of the application outside of EC2. It is a Ruby Application.

  %div.project.devsync
